  "decision_conditions": [
    "Reason : 1 - The proposed two storey side extension, by reason of it's parallel siting in relation to a facing first floor flank habitable room window at No. 47 Brook Drive alongside it's lack sufficient separation from this window and elevated height in respect to this neighbouring window, would appear unneighbourly and visually intrusive when viewed from this neighbouring window, unduly detracting from the overall level of outlook and visual amenity afforded to the impacted habitable room. The proposal would thereby be contrary to the high quality design aspirations of the National Planning Policy Framework (2023), Policy D3.D(7) of The London Plan (2021), Policies DM1 C, DM1 D (d), (e) and (f) of the Harrow Development Management Policies Local Plan (2013), and the adopted Supplementary Planning Document: Residential Design Guide (2010)."
